reviewText: watched again and again, great stuff.
This is a wonderful series but I would love to see it on dvd. I have the first set on dvd and it is great.

I sent these tapes to my parents as a gift and they loved them. They've watched them more than once, delighting in small elements missed the first viewing. Maigret is better than most TV today and is worthwhile for those who want to sit and watch a show.
